  <div class="tt-about-us tt-section" id="about-us">
    <img class="tt-swirl-icon" src="images/tt-swirl-yellow.png" alt="Tara Thai Swirl Icon">
    <h1 class="h1-invert">About Us</h1>
    <h2 class="h2-invert">เกี่ยวกับเรา</h2>
    <p class="invert">
      A culinary experience in Thai cuisine is synonymous with a journey through
      Thai culture; every presentation is aesthetic, elegant and indeed graceful.
    </p>
    <p class="invert">
      In Tara Thai, we firmly believe in upholding a tradition which has since
      propelled Thai food to the forefront of worldwide cuisines. Indeed, it is
      our utmost intention to provide dining guests with an experience immersed
      in authenticity which is true to the essence of Thai cuisine.
    </p>
    <p class="invert">
      At Tara Thai, our motto is to serve and we shall endeavour to make your
      visit to us a truly enjoyable occasion.
    </p>
